## 4. Key Root Configuration Files (Shared)
*   `app.json` / `app.config.js` — Expo client configuration module.
*   `babel.config.js` — Babel transpiler compiler configurations.
*   `eslint.config.js` — Linter and code styling compliance rules.
*   `metro.config.js` — React Native Metro packager options.
*   `tailwind.config.js` — NativeWind/Tailwind styling layout parameters.
*   `tsconfig.json` — TypeScript configuration parameters.
